{"PageNumber":38,"Angle":0,"RotatedAngle":0,"Height":2376,"Width":1836,"OriginHeight":0,"OriginWidth":0,"Elements":[{"Index":0,"Type":"Discard_type","Text":"6/4/26, 8:47 PM","Level":0,"Polygon":{"LeftBottom":{"X":66,"Y":69},"LeftTop":{"X":66,"Y":42},"RightBottom":{"X":242,"Y":69},"RightTop":{"X":242,"Y":42}},"InsetImageName":"","Elements":null,"ImagePath":"","group_id":-1,"group_type":""},{"Index":1,"Type":"Discard_type","Text":"(23) Activity| Duncan Rogoff| LinkedIn","Level":0,"Polygon":{"LeftBottom":{"X":834,"Y":74},"LeftTop":{"X":834,"Y":42},"RightBottom":{"X":1254,"Y":74},"RightTop":{"X":1254,"Y":42}},"InsetImageName":"","Elements":null,"ImagePath":"","group_id":-1,"group_type":""},{"Index":2,"Type":"figure","Text":"![](193,153,356,222)","Level":0,"Polygon":{"LeftBottom":{"X":193,"Y":222},"LeftTop":{"X":193,"Y":153},"RightBottom":{"X":356,"Y":222},"RightTop":{"X":356,"Y":153}},"InsetImageName":"","Elements":null,"ImagePath":"images/43be30063d7bd3189abf2b506b20e785-image.png","group_id":-1,"group_type":""},{"Index":3,"Type":"title","Text":"Stop losing 6hrs a day 10+ hours back.Free.","Level":0,"Polygon":{"LeftBottom":{"X":398,"Y":366},"LeftTop":{"X":398,"Y":240},"RightBottom":{"X":987,"Y":366},"RightTop":{"X":987,"Y":240}},"InsetImageName":"","Elements":null,"ImagePath":"","group_id":-1,"group_type":""},{"Index":4,"Type":"title","Text":"The Job Automation Audit","Level":0,"Polygon":{"LeftBottom":{"X":247,"Y":509},"LeftTop":{"X":247,"Y":467},"RightBottom":{"X":749,"Y":509},"RightTop":{"X":749,"Y":467}},"InsetImageName":"","Elements":null,"ImagePath":"","group_id":-1,"group_type":""},{"Index":5,"Type":"paragraph","Text":"Find the 10+ hours hiding in your workweek and hand them off to Al- so you only touch the work that actually grows revenue.","Level":0,"Polygon":{"LeftBottom":{"X":247,"Y":584},"LeftTop":{"X":247,"Y":532},"RightBottom":{"X":1133,"Y":584},"RightTop":{"X":1133,"Y":532}},"InsetImageName":"","Elements":null,"ImagePath":"","group_id":-1,"group_type":""},{"Index":6,"Type":"title","Text":"Read This First","Level":0,"Polygon":{"LeftBottom":{"X":247,"Y":685},"LeftTop":{"X":247,"Y":653},"RightBottom":{"X":467,"Y":685},"RightTop":{"X":467,"Y":653}},"InsetImageName":"","Elements":null,"ImagePath":"","group_id":-1,"group_type":""},{"Index":7,"Type":"paragraph","Text":"Two years ago I was doing everything myself. Research, writing, scheduling, inbox management, reporting-![all](248,740,277,759)all of it. I was working 50-hour weeks and barely breaking even on the things that actually mattered. Revenue was stuck. Growth was stuck. I was the bottleneck.","Level":0,"Polygon":{"LeftBottom":{"X":247,"Y":792},"LeftTop":{"X":247,"Y":705},"RightBottom":{"X":1123,"Y":792},"RightTop":{"X":1123,"Y":705}},"InsetImageName":"","Elements":null,"ImagePath":"images/7a44aa8344b59edd113eee87bd7ca212-image.png","group_id":-1,"group_type":""},{"Index":8,"Type":"paragraph","Text":"Then I started auditing my time like a ruthless accountant. Task by task. Hour by hour. I asked one question![about](248,842,289,866)about everything I did: does a human need to do this, or can a machine do it better and faster?","Level":0,"Polygon":{"LeftBottom":{"X":247,"Y":866},"LeftTop":{"X":247,"Y":809},"RightBottom":{"X":1106,"Y":866},"RightTop":{"X":1106,"Y":809}},"InsetImageName":"","Elements":null,"ImagePath":"images/73f1dfc0617749c2665a5e530a0569df-image.png","group_id":-1,"group_type":""},{"Index":9,"Type":"paragraph","Text":"![The](248,887,294,908)answer was uncomfortable. More than 60% of what I was doing every day required zero human judgment.![It just](248,917,294,938)required time.Time I was trading for tasks that a$5/day Al stack could handle permanently.","Level":0,"Polygon":{"LeftBottom":{"X":247,"Y":940},"LeftTop":{"X":247,"Y":883},"RightBottom":{"X":1133,"Y":940},"RightTop":{"X":1133,"Y":883}},"InsetImageName":"","Elements":null,"ImagePath":"images/6300132fc6433cdcb45a0cbfdb20f432-image.png","group_id":-1,"group_type":""},{"Index":10,"Type":"paragraph","Text":"![I built](248,959,294,982)6 Al sub-agents to run my content pipeline. I cut my research time by 80%. I went from 0 to 110K+![follow](248,989,294,1014)owers across channels in under 12 months and generated$150K+ in revenue directly from content-while![my Al](248,1021,294,1044)stack ran most of the operation.","Level":0,"Polygon":{"LeftBottom":{"X":247,"Y":1041},"LeftTop":{"X":247,"Y":955},"RightBottom":{"X":1133,"Y":1041},"RightTop":{"X":1133,"Y":955}},"InsetImageName":"","Elements":null,"ImagePath":"images/2c6ab3e41b44df93a898ffe55424b629-image.png","group_id":-1,"group_type":""},{"Index":11,"Type":"paragraph","Text":"![This](248,1063,294,1086)audit is the exact process I used. It takes about 20 minutes to complete. When you are done, you will have ked list of tasks to automate, the prompts to start automating them today, and a clear picture of how many![](248,1095,294,1148)hours you are leaving on the table every single week.","Level":0,"Polygon":{"LeftBottom":{"X":247,"Y":1148},"LeftTop":{"X":247,"Y":1059},"RightBottom":{"X":1140,"Y":1148},"RightTop":{"X":1140,"Y":1059}},"InsetImageName":"","Elements":null,"ImagePath":"images/91e6349032389bff07bf61d70f7fd8fd-image.png","group_id":-1,"group_type":""},{"Index":12,"Type":"title","Text":"How to Use This Document","Level":0,"Polygon":{"LeftBottom":{"X":247,"Y":1200},"LeftTop":{"X":247,"Y":1173},"RightBottom":{"X":564,"Y":1200},"RightTop":{"X":564,"Y":1173}},"InsetImageName":"","Elements":null,"ImagePath":"","group_id":-1,"group_type":""},{"Index":13,"Type":"paragraph","Text":"1. Work through Part 1 first. Dump every repeating task you do in a week onto the audit table. Do not filter yet-just list.","Level":0,"Polygon":{"LeftBottom":{"X":252,"Y":1272},"LeftTop":{"X":252,"Y":1215},"RightBottom":{"X":1138,"Y":1272},"RightTop":{"X":1138,"Y":1215}},"InsetImageName":"","Elements":null,"ImagePath":"","group_id":-1,"group_type":""},{"Index":14,"Type":"paragraph","Text":"2. Score each task using the three criteria in Part 2. This tells you what to automate first.","Level":0,"Polygon":{"LeftBottom":{"X":252,"Y":1306},"LeftTop":{"X":252,"Y":1282},"RightBottom":{"X":965,"Y":1306},"RightTop":{"X":965,"Y":1282}},"InsetImageName":"","Elements":null,"ImagePath":"","group_id":-1,"group_type":""},{"Index":15,"Type":"paragraph","Text":"3. Use the copy-paste prompts in Part 3 to start handing off your top 3 tasks to Al today.","Level":0,"Polygon":{"LeftBottom":{"X":252,"Y":1343},"LeftTop":{"X":252,"Y":1316},"RightBottom":{"X":960,"Y":1343},"RightTop":{"X":960,"Y":1316}},"InsetImageName":"","Elements":null,"ImagePath":"","group_id":-1,"group_type":""},{"Index":16,"Type":"paragraph","Text":"Play","Level":0,"Polygon":{"LeftBottom":{"X":150,"Y":1467},"LeftTop":{"X":150,"Y":1433},"RightBottom":{"X":220,"Y":1467},"RightTop":{"X":220,"Y":1433}},"InsetImageName":"","Elements":null,"ImagePath":"","group_id":-1,"group_type":""},{"Index":17,"Type":"paragraph","Text":" Media Media is loading","Level":0,"Polygon":{"LeftBottom":{"X":150,"Y":1494},"LeftTop":{"X":150,"Y":1465},"RightBottom":{"X":319,"Y":1494},"RightTop":{"X":319,"Y":1465}},"InsetImageName":"","Elements":null,"ImagePath":"","group_id":-1,"group_type":""},{"Index":18,"Type":"figure","Text":"![](150,1492,220,1549)","Level":0,"Polygon":{"LeftBottom":{"X":150,"Y":1549},"LeftTop":{"X":150,"Y":1492},"RightBottom":{"X":220,"Y":1549},"RightTop":{"X":220,"Y":1492}},"InsetImageName":"","Elements":[{"Index":0,"Type":"figure_text","Text":"Play","Level":0,"Polygon":{"LeftBottom":{"X":162,"Y":1523},"LeftTop":{"X":162,"Y":1496},"RightBottom":{"X":211,"Y":1523},"RightTop":{"X":211,"Y":1496}},"InsetImageName":"","Elements":null,"ImagePath":"","group_id":-1,"group_type":""},{"Index":1,"Type":"figure_text","Text":"P","Level":0,"Polygon":{"LeftBottom":{"X":162,"Y":1547},"LeftTop":{"X":162,"Y":1518},"RightBottom":{"X":184,"Y":1547},"RightTop":{"X":184,"Y":1518}},"InsetImageName":"","Elements":null,"ImagePath":"","group_id":-1,"group_type":""}],"ImagePath"